1 WHEREAS, the 2026 Italian Festival is being held April 24-26, 2026; and
2 WHEREAS, the organizers, volunteers, and royal court of the 2026 Italian Festival
3 in Tickfaw merit a sincere and heartfelt measure of commendation for the tremendous pride
4 and honor that this wonderful annual event brings to the citizens of Louisiana.
5 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
6 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend the Italian Festival Royal Court on the
7 occasion of the 2026 Italian Festival in Tickfaw, Louisiana, and does hereby recognize this
8 special event as an integral part of the celebration of Italian-American culture and history
9 in the state of Louisiana.
